history.text: Hey
Hi there
How was the movie?

Batman vs Superman

Do you mind spoilers?
It's fine I am always still ok with watching something after spoilers. :D

O I still thought the lex's kid is dumb and I feel like the actor they picked to play him was blah.

Did they at lest make cool batman gadgets
 ?
They have Batman in power-armor and with a Kryptonite spear.
But the gadgets aren't front and center

I still want them just to take some of the animated movies and make them live action like super man all star boom! done perfect
 move.

yea when you get time check them out 1000% better

then..
